commit.message:
CI: Ensure code coverage reporting will work in February 2022 and beyond

See https://github.com/gap-actions/process-coverage/issues/10
Switch CI to use GitHub Actions

Fix problems with the Gua05 BibTeX entry.

- Fix a misplaced comma that masked all but the author field
- Use the correct separator for multiple authors
- Use an em-dash instead of a hyphen in the title
- Remove a trailing period from the title
Disable maintainer flag for David Joyner
Add the GAP Team as package maintainer
Don't use undocumented extra args to InstallGlobalFunction
Updated URL of David Joyner's personal homepage

tests: change variables Div, Cones, Rays to div, cones, rays

This avoids conflicts with package using the former identifiers
for operations.

Resolves #7

Version 1.9.2

Use package name in lowercase in various URLs
Use AutoDoc to generate title page

Rename toric_gapdoc.gap -> makedoc.g

This matches the convention most other packages follow
